data.title: Dean's List
data.meta_description: The College of Education Dean’s List recognizes academic achievement within a single semester.
data.text:
The College of Education Dean’s List recognizes academic achievement within a single semester. Being named to the list recognizes the honorees’ academic achievements during the past semester in which they have been in good academic standing, an undergraduate, matriculated and achieved a 3.50 GPA or greater based on a minimum of 12 units of credit for courses in which letter grades were assigned. The Dean's List honorees’ outstanding scholarship furthers the high reputation for academic excellence enjoyed by their program, the College of Education and the University.

Please note that the dean's list is published 6–8 weeks after the semester. If you have requested your name be kept confidential in my.SDSU, your name will not appear on this webpage.
